Summary: Saw a rapid moving thing low in the sky with blinking lights. My phone stopped working and my radio got staticy.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving home around 9 PM Central time and I saw a rapidly moving figure in the sky that had blinking lights. It made my phone unable to call or recieve anything and my radio became very staticy. The object disappeared. I assume it teleported or something.
